<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="27">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="27">Habitat in Europae and Americae septentrionalis (lectotype, designated by Soreng in 2000: 255: LINN (LINN-87.41!)).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
